{
  "texts": [
    "It signifies that human agents are not the only memory prosumers anymore.",
    "With the decrease of active remembrance among human agents (i.e.",
    "as part of the process of greying memory; Hoskins and Halstead 2021), this transformation can make robots key actors in retrieving and producing memories.",
    "Such production can take various forms: for instance, robotic agents can communicate with each other in order to construct memories about human individuals (e.g.",
    "in the form of personal digital twins; de Kerckhove 2021)."
  ]
}